author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
"Elevator Operator" by Electric Callboy was released on 24 January, so I know I'm late to this. I blame Transport For London and door trouble at a stately home. It's also late posting on YouTube - copyright restrictions were brutal on this one, so to watch the whole video, visit here first: https://youtu.be/BiP0FpY88E4?si=XpOi_wqt_dHAF3Uu

The new Darkness album comes out next month,  you can pre-order 'Dreams On Toast' on CD, vinyl or cassette here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

The Darkness are also going on tour across the UK in March, tickets are on sale here: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

To talk to me on Patreon:  http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

#reaction #musicreview #ElectricCallboy
title: Love In An Elevator? Going Down With Electric Callboy
